     1→/// Level 4 — TrueColor renderer (24-bit RGB, double-line box, column layout).
     2→///
     3→/// Uses `╔═╗║╚═╝` double-line borders. Two-column layout at width >= 100
     4→/// (headers and boxes sized to column width). Progress bar with per-cell RGB
     5→/// gradient (amber #B8690F → green #1E8A45 as percentage rises).
     6→/// Card separators within section boxes use rounded single-line (╭─╮│╰╯).
